{"tid":1461490,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[教學] 自己的文宣自己做（基礎）","createTime":"2019-08-13T07:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T08:13:19.000Z","uid":139173,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5ebb0b0b1a498f878e3739b90c69dcfdb7d4ceae","tid":1461490,"uid":139173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mQdBFB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mQdBFB.jpg&h=c9d67bd5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">1．前言</span></strong><br />\n本人係連登第二次出文。我只係一人團隊，好多野都考慮不周。有好多熱心巴絲想整文宣但無咩概念，所以我整左個基礎心得分享，同埋template 連用法(詳見最底)， 比大家參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">2．概念</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>＝2a：讀者＝</strong></span><br />\n首先，做文宣要搞清楚 <strong><ins>讀者係邊個</ins></strong> ，呢樣野完全影響文宣內容。例如「警察」，比巴絲睇你可以叫<strong>「克警」</strong>；比藍絲中立派要用<strong>「失控警員」</strong>。文宣一定令讀者放低介心，先可以做到宣傳效果，否則你後面幾天花龍鳳，對唔住都係圍爐晒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>＝2b：材料＝</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmdbone.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnmdbone.png&h=29100fd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文宣四寶：紙、圖、標題、內容 （同連登開post一樣）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">／紙／</span></strong><br />\n貼牆愈大愈好，可以考慮4張a4合做1張a3。派街唔好太大張，可以考慮b5／半張a4<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">／圖／</span></strong><br />\n請誇張清楚，必要時可以用指嘴，圈圈等方式<strong><ins>標示重點</ins></strong>。同時可以加上一句<strong><ins>簡單caption</ins></strong>描述一下張圖講咩。經費許可請彩print ＞用highlight pen＞黑白。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">／標題／</span></strong><br />\n請放<strong><ins>最多時間思考</ins></strong>一個好標題。標題要交待發生事件，同埋得出結論。舉例義士爆眼單野，要<strong><ins>交待警察使用過度暴力，結論得出政府警察正仆街。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n第一版<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: orange;\">「失控警察實彈爆眼；女示威者永久失明」</span></em><br />\n＃失控 (降低警方威信) ＃實彈爆眼 (暴力) ＃女示威者永久失明 (事件及嚇人結果)<br />\n<br />\n最終版<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: orange;\">「失控警察濫用私刑；實彈槍瞄頭爆眼」</span></em><br />\n＃失控 (降低警方威信)  ＃濫用私刑 (暴力) ＃實彈槍瞄頭爆眼(流暢動作交待事件)<br />\n<br />\n我故意刪走女示威者，避免藍絲中立派先入為主：<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><em>先有示威者生事＞警察合理開槍＞示威者自作自受＞所以抵死</em></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">內容／</span></strong><br />\n內容都要交待更多細節，最後一定要有一個<strong><ins>你要帶出既message</ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n例如義士爆眼單野：<br />\n「香港政府縱容警方無視工作指示，濫用暴力，嚴重違反專業操守」<br />\n<br />\n整張文宣要令藍絲中立派睇完<strong><ins>質疑政府處理失當，警方失職 </ins></strong>。唔好期望佢地一下子轉槍頭屌政府，只要令藍絲中立派同情示威者，開始質疑佢地眼中全能既政府，文宣已經成功達成任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住我地要政府係藍絲中立派心中失信，咁我地表達訴求就會少左好多社區阻力。注：以上用左藍絲中立派文宣做例。我好欣賞其他海報文宣巴絲，自己未有咁既能力同時間，但好支持你地用靚poster團結我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">3．其他</span></strong><br />\n－藍絲中立派睇既文宣字<strong><ins>一定要大隻</ins></strong>，佢地對眼係自動過濾細字<br />\n－機場遊客文宣一定要有英文<br />\n－（有待大家補充）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"> 4．工具</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>＝4a：我做既Templat＝</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRn3Y6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRn3Y6E.jpg&h=c397fb10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKpemj0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKpemj0.jpg&h=9796e7df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">／google drive下載／</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1elaqtGFJgzGFcOF9S7cC45cSfKXQryp7/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1elaqtGFJgzGFcOF9S7cC45cSfKXQryp7%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=9a538def\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1elaqtGFJgzGFcOF9S7cC45cSfKXQryp7/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>＝4b：編輯加字工具＝</strong></span><br />\n可用AI、PS、Indesign、小畫家等工具<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">／Online_Photoshop／</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.onlinephotoshopfree.info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onlinephotoshopfree.info%2F&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=8a08a4ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.onlinephotoshopfree.info/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">／我做既教學／</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nDBYkvATApg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnDBYkvATApg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbzizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=4cf8bb4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nDBYkvATApg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n＃香港加油 ＃不分化不割蓆不篤灰 ＃五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4b86b82147f38d7daf1e3bc140a202b3238bab","tid":1461490,"uid":37495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:00:53.000Z","msg":"推 721 811"},{"pid":"a3bdfc916f1980de1605e8fe794829e100eb1528","tid":1461490,"uid":265889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"ching你個圖細字寫:<br />\n全面落實雙真普選<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">私刑</span></strong>?????"},{"pid":"89ddaf868f653e1d20a69c6e7d51e8306f6b33c5","tid":1461490,"uid":139173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3bdfc916f1980de1605e8fe794829e100eb1528","tid":14614